<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include">
    <sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
        <access>public</access>
        <active>true</active>
        <api_name>global.ResolutionFrameworkClassificationTypeChoices</api_name>
        <caller_access/>
        <client_callable>false</client_callable>
        <description>Choice list for Error Framework Error classification field </description>
        <name>ResolutionFrameworkClassificationTypeChoices</name>
        <script><![CDATA[var ResolutionFrameworkClassificationTypeChoices = Class.create();
ResolutionFrameworkClassificationTypeChoices.prototype = {
	process: function() {
		var supportedChoices = new SNC.KMFErrorFrameworkAPI().getSupportedErrorClassifications();
		var choiceList = new GlideChoiceList();
		var jsonObj = JSON.parse(supportedChoices);
		for (var value in jsonObj)
			choiceList.add(value, jsonObj[value]);

		return choiceList;
	},

	type: 'ResolutionFrameworkClassificationTypeChoices'
};]]></script>
